span=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-brown\">%</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:C-ration.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"C-ration.png\" src=\"/images/4/45/C-ration.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>名称\n</th>\n<td>C-口粮\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>基础价\n</th>\n<td>20 <a href=\"/wiki/%E9%87%91%E5%B8%81\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"金币\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>营养值\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E5%80%BC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"营养值 (page does not exist)\">300</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>食用所需回合数\n</th>\n<td>1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>重量\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%87%8D%E9%87%8F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"重量 (page does not exist)\">10</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>行为\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%A1%8C%E4%B8%BA&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"行为 (page does not exist)\">绝对素食</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>C-口粮</b>（C-ration）是<a href=\"/index.php?title=NetHack/zh-CN&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"NetHack/zh-CN (page does not exist)\">NetHack</a>中的一种<a href=\"/wiki/%E5%8F%AF%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"可食用品\">可食用品</a>。它属于<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"素食 (page does not exist)\">素食</a>，适合于<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"绝对素食 (page does not exist)\">绝对素食</a>行为。\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">生成</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">描述</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">策略</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">历史</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#.E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">起源</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#.E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">消息</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#SLASH.27EM\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">SLASH'EM</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#SpliceHack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">SpliceHack</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#.E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">引用及注释</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"生成\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.94.9F.E6.88.90\">生成</span></h2>\n<p>C-口粮不会随机生成。<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%B2%A9%E5%BE%B7%E5%86%9B%E5%9B%A2&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"岩德军团 (page does not exist)\">岩德军团</a>的士兵们在生成时有<sup>1</sup>&#8260;<sub>2</sub>的概率<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%80%AA%E7%89%A9%E8%B5%B7%E5%A7%8B%E7%89%A9%E5%93%81&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"怪物起始物品 (page does not exist)\">携带</a>一份C-口粮<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"描述\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.8F.8F.E8.BF.B0\">描述</span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%A8\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"食用\">食用</a>C-口粮会获得300<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E5%80%BC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"营养值 (page does not exist)\">营养值</a>，和<a href=\"/wiki/K-%E5%8F%A3%E7%B2%AE\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"K-口粮\">K-口粮</a>相似，C-口粮只需1回合即可吃完。C-可以用于<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A9%AF%E6%9C%8D&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"驯服 (page does not exist)\">驯服</a><a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%AE%B6%E7%95%9C&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"家畜 (page does not exist)\">家畜</a>类的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%8C%AB%E7%A7%91%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"猫科动物 (page does not exist)\">猫科动物</a>和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%8A%AC%E7%A7%91%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"犬科动物 (page does not exist)\">犬科动物</a>，也可以用来安抚家畜类<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E9%A9%AC%E7%A7%91%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"马科动物 (page does not exist)\">马科动物</a>。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"策略\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E7.AD.96.E7.95.A5\">策略</span></h2>\n<p>C-口粮很适合在紧急情况下快速补充营养，而且你可以在清理<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%85%B5%E8%90%A5&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"兵营 (page does not exist)\">兵营</a>（例如在<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%90%95%E5%BA%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%A0%A1%E5%9E%92&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"吕底人堡垒 (page does not exist)\">吕底人堡垒</a>和<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E5%9F%8E%E5%A0%A1&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"城堡 (page does not exist)\">城堡</a>里）时大量获得C-口粮。K-口粮的效果和C-口粮基本相同，但K-口粮的营养值更高——因此玩家在为<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%98%9F%E7%95%8C%E4%BD%8D%E9%9D%A2&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"星界位面 (page does not exist)\">星界位面</a>作准备时更倾向于选择K-口粮。\n</p><p>C-口粮对于无法进行<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E6%97%A0%E9%A5%A5%E9%A5%BF%E6%96%BD%E6%B3%95&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"无饥饿施法 (page does not exist)\">无饥饿施法</a>的<a href=\"/index.php?title=%E7%BB%9D%E5%AF%B9%E7%B4%A0%E9%A3%9F&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"绝对素食 (page does not exist)\">绝对素食</a>施法者角色而言很实用。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"历史\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.8E.86.E5.8F.B2\">历史</span></h2>\n<p>C-口粮首次在<a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_2.3e\" title=\"NetHack 2.3e\">NetHack 2.3e</a>加入游戏。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"起源\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E8.B5.B7.E6.BA.90\">起源</span></h2>\n<div class=\"noprint sidebox\">\n<div style=\"float: left;\"><div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"维基百科\"><img alt=\"维基百科\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png/50px-Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/f/f8/Fair-use-wikipedia-logo.png 1.5x\" /></a></div></div>\n<div style=\"margin-left: 60px;\"><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/zh:Main_Page\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:zh:Main Page\">维基百科</a>相关条目：\n<div style=\"margin-left: 10px;\"><i><b><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Search/C-ration\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Special:Search/C-ration\">C-ration </a></b></i></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>现实中，C-口粮是1938&#x2014;1958期间的美国军队口粮，在二战中大量使用，后被<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meal,_Combat,_Individual\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:Meal, Combat, Individual\">MCI口粮</a>取代，但美军士兵们仍然习惯性地称呼MCI为“C-口粮”，直到1981年它被<a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/zh:MRE%E5%8F%A3%E7%B2%AE\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:zh:MRE口粮\">MRE口粮</a>取代为止。\n</p><p>每顿C-口粮包含两个罐头，即一份内含面包的“B”餐和一份内含肉的“M”餐，每日的口粮配给包含三顿这样的口粮。事实上，即使是“B”餐都不符合绝对素食的标准。C-口粮的菜单很单调，因此在军队中不受欢迎<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>。\n</p><p>“C-口粮”名称中的“C”实际没有任何意义，只是当时军用口粮名称的代号，与之并列的还有“A-口粮”（基地食堂的自助军用餐）和“B-口粮”（战地厨房的公共餐）。\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"消息\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E6.B6.88.E6.81.AF\">消息</span></h2>\n<dl><dt><span id=\".E8.BF.99.E4.B8.AAC-.E5.8F.A3.E7.B2.AE.E6.98.AF.E6.97.A0.E5.91.B3.E7.9A.84.E3.80.82\">这个C-口粮是无味的。</span>（This C-ration is bland.）</dt>\n<dd>你吃下了一份非诅咒的C-口粮。</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Variants\">Variants</span></h2>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>此条目或段落的部分内容需要翻译。</b><br />\n您可以帮助我们<a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=C-ration/zh-CN&amp;action=edit\"><b>翻译此页面</b></a>，但<b>请勿使用机器翻译</b>。\n</p>\n</div>\n<h3><span id=\"SLASH'EM\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"SLASH.27EM\">SLASH'EM</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/SLASH%27EM\" title=\"SLASH&#39;EM\">SLASH'EM</a>, C-rations can be <a href=\"/wiki/Upgraded\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Upgraded\">upgraded</a> into <a href=\"/wiki/Cram_ration\" title=\"Cram ration\">cram rations</a> or <a href=\"/wiki/Food_ration\" title=\"Food ration\">food rations</a>. This also applies to <a href=\"/wiki/SlashTHEM\" title=\"SlashTHEM\">SlashTHEM</a>.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"SpliceHack\">SpliceHack</span></h3>\n<p>In <a href=\"/wiki/SpliceHack\" title=\"SpliceHack\">SpliceHack</a>, a C-ration can be combined with a food ration at a <a href=\"/wiki/Furnace\" title=\"Furnace\">furnace</a> to create a K-ration.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"引用及注释\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".E5.BC.95.E7.94.A8.E5.8F.8A.E6.B3.A8.E9.87.8A\">引用及注释</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/NetHack/NetHack/blob/NetHack-3.6.7_Released/src/makemon.c#L668\">src/makemon.c in NetHack 3.6.7, line 668</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.usarmymodels.com/ARTICLES/Rations/crations.html\">http://www.usarmymodels.com/ARTICLES/Rations/crations.html</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\"><img alt=\"此条目的内容已同步至NetHack 3.6.7。详细信息请点击此处。\" src=\"/images/f/f7/Nh367-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926182714\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.038 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.052 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 428/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 2509/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4771/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 801/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 814/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   35.867      1 -total\n 19.20%    6.886      1 Template:Languages\n 13.34%    4.783      1 Template:Nethack-367/zh-CN\n 13.21%    4.738      1 Template:Refsrc\n 12.97%    4.653      5 Template:Languages/Lang\n 10.71%    3.843      1 Template:Comestible/zh-CN\n  9.67%    3.469      1 Template:Version_icon/zh-CN\n  7.62%    2.734      1 Template:Message/zh-CN\n  7.27%    2.608      1 Template:Wikipedia/zh-CN\n  6.40%    2.296      1 Template:Organic_color\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wikihackdb:pcache:idhash:40516-0!canonical and timestamp 20240926182714 and revision id 174942\n -->\n</div></div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=C-ration/zh-CN&amp;oldid=174942\">https://nethackwiki.com/index.php?title=C-ration/zh-CN&amp;oldid=174942</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>